{#-
  Auth-AccountLocked — terminal account-lock-out pattern (Ring 3 S3.1b).

  Composes `_auth-shell` (title null — inner Empty owns the h1) + Empty
  (lg, h1, icon=alert-triangle substitut OQ-57b) + Button × 1-2 (primary
  Contact-support + optional secondary Back-to-login).

  Pure server-rendered terminal page (OQ-55). 0 Stimulus controller. The
  consumer's auth back-end determines when an account becomes locked
  (typically after N failed Auth-Login attempts beyond the soft
  `rateLimitedNotice` threshold) and surfaces this pattern on the
  /account/locked route.

  Relationship to Error-RateLimited :
    Auth-AccountLocked is the **terminal graduation** of the transient
    rate-limit. Error-RateLimited shows "retry in X min" (recoverable) ;
    Auth-AccountLocked shows "contact support" (terminal until manual
    unlock).

  Icon choice : `alert-triangle` is the OQ-57b substitut for the missing
  `lock` / `shield` curated-set icon. Same visual signal as
  Error-RateLimited.

  See `docs/specs/ring3/Auth-AccountLocked.md` for full spec.
-#}

{%- set title             = title             | default('theme.auth.account-locked.title'|trans) -%}
{%- set body              = body              | default('theme.auth.account-locked.body'|trans) -%}
{%- set supportLabel      = supportLabel      | default('theme.auth.account-locked.support-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set supportHref       = supportHref       | default('#') -%}
{%- set backToLoginLabel  = backToLoginLabel  | default('theme.auth.account-locked.back-to-login-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set backToLoginHref   = backToLoginHref   | default(null) -%}
{%- set htmlId            = htmlId            | default('cremona-auth-account-locked') -%}
{%- set className         = className         | default('') -%}

{% embed '@cremona/components/_auth-shell/_auth-shell.html.twig' with {
  title: null,
  htmlId: htmlId,
  variant: 'default',
  className: ('cremona-auth-account-locked ' ~ className)|trim,
} %}
  {% block content %}
    {% embed '@cremona/components/empty/empty.html.twig' with {
      title: title,
      body: body,
      icon: 'alert-triangle',
      size: 'lg',
      titleLevel: 'h1',
      htmlId: htmlId ~ '-empty',
    } %}
      {% block actions %}
        {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
          label: supportLabel,
          variant: 'primary',
          size: 'md',
          href: supportHref,
        } %}
        {% if backToLoginHref %}
          {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
            label: backToLoginLabel,
            variant: 'ghost',
            size: 'md',
            href: backToLoginHref,
            iconLeading: 'arrow-left',
          } %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endblock %}
    {% endembed %}
  {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
